"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Guild W is the first on-chain e-sports team, incubated by [MarrowDAO](https://twitter.com/marrowdao). The main members are Solidity developers, node operators, blockchain game players and investment analysts. All of them are loyal players of the Dark Forest.\\n\\nW stands for waterdrop. In *The Three-Body Problem*, waterdrop is a cosmic detector made of strong interacting materials. Its surface is absolutely convex curved, and the temperature is absolutely zero. One waterdrop can destroy most of humanity's armed forces in space.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ebfe7d6a-296c-4bbf-af3c-c5f30c6cbd32.png?height=1200&width=2400)\\n\\nGuild W believes in the future of native blockchain games and in the power of technology. \\n\\nWe are building a professional e-sports team with both software developers and game players. We hope our guild may possess different perspectives at the same time, as visionary as waterdrops. We will uphold the aim of peaceful development and help real blockchain games to grow and prosper.\\n\\nRecently, Guild W has received funding from Yuanyuzhou Ventures, Evernew Capital, DAppChaser and EM3DAO, and ecological support from ChainNews, RhizomeDAO and MAODAO.\\n\\nThere will be a bounty plan to reward our members for their contributions, including open-source plugins, game tutorials and joint warfare.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/d2132840-7a8f-461f-8766-8903883a9773.png?height=400&width=800)\\n\\nAnyone can support MarrowDAO and Guild W by collecting this article's NFT. The artwork is created by Lin Chen, a Chinese fractal artist with over a decade of generative art experience. Lin Chen is also a science fiction fan who loves *The Three-Body Problem*.\\n\\n## Guild W: 首个链上电竞团队\\n\\nGuild W 是第一支链上电竞团队，由 MarrowDAO 孵化。主要成员为 Solidity 开发者、节点运维、链游玩家和投资分析师。所有成员都是黑暗森林的忠实玩家。\\n\\nW 的意思是 waterdrop，即“水滴”。《三体》中，水滴是由强互作用力（SIM）材料制成的宇宙探测器，其表面绝对光滑，温度为绝对零度。仅一个水滴就能摧毁人类大部分的太空武装力量。 \\n\\nGuild W 相信原生区块链游戏的未来，相信技术的力量。\\n\\n我们建立了一个由开发者和玩家组成的专业电子竞技团队，希望它兼具多重视角，如水滴一样，高瞻远瞩。与此同时，我们将秉持和平发展的宗旨，帮助真正的区块链游戏不断成长，走向繁荣。\\n\\n近期，Guild W 获得了元宇宙资本、恒新资本、DAppChaser 和 EM3DAO 的赞助支持，以及链闻、RhizomeDAO 和 MAODAO 的生态支持。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/7b7ab421-a97e-4bb5-9974-4f58fab14df6.png?height=400&width=800)\\n\\n我们将设立社区奖金，创建专属 NFT，用于奖励我们成员的贡献，包括开源插件、游戏攻略、联合作战等。\\n\\n任何人都可以通过收集这篇文章的 NFT 来支持 MarrowDAO 和 Guild W。NFT艺术品由中国分形艺术家林晨创作，他拥有十年以上的生成艺术创作经验，同时是一位喜欢《三体》的科幻迷。\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1628936086,\"title\":\"Guild W: The first on-chain e-sports team\",\"publication\":\"buidl\"},\"digest\":\"0I9oYGGKOxDrb2m8OjubyxjU4wYbs9Zp49c0IO2OwUc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x65946FfB5FAbE6d4D02F826699204336b42D436F\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"iap-JwDUOheClwrohN0Pf0m-w0tKeWDg46Pnh0DoTYM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"J4s1XOfCWyUBdkAbz2B6t5JTG2xCPhbXmzGEFx2Nu5I\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ojmdyS1MNzQpZUgil1qBgPsRG-8rVsGq3HuWTDZz-Gv_FdwNx6-r_j8hKrfP2Vni7aLaZJYsiNOYMySNeI0u_g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x10432660aa2ceb77a9b584491af01541afc1b51f9f1b86ce27520ac94f36383f14dfb0331e5761e8241fac5f59edfe27e7ee84d59bf09719f8ef21cd41eb0b291c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on buidl.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"iap-JwDUOheClwrohN0Pf0m-w0tKeWDg46Pnh0DoTYM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"J4s1XOfCWyUBdkAbz2B6t5JTG2xCPhbXmzGEFx2Nu5I\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"0I9oYGGKOxDrb2m8OjubyxjU4wYbs9Zp49c0IO2OwUc\"}"